title: RQ: Sting - It's Probably Me (Dutch Treat MP3 + FLAC version)
description:
On Request: MP3 and FLAC version:

Some people complained (yes they do) about the sound quality of the B009 Playlist. I agree it could and should be better. Sting deserves only the best. So I tried to find better recordings than I already had. Did not find any. So for these people I included a FLAC version that is slightly better.... Enjoy,

PS For other Sting (Duets) songs, see A060 Roxanne.
